{"id":63860,"date":"2016-08-08T08:18:59","date_gmt":"2016-08-08T15:18:59","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/?p=63860"},"modified":"2016-08-08T08:18:59","modified_gmt":"2016-08-08T15:18:59","slug":"kadenze-columbia-berklee","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/kadenze-columbia-berklee\/","title":{"rendered":"Columbia University And Berklee College Of Music Join Kadenze"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Kadenze, a MOOC platform geared towards Arts education, has racked up two more partners \u2014 Columbia University and Berklee College of Music. This means that Kadenze now has a total of 26 partner institutions, including Stanford, Princeton, and CalArts.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Kadenze-Partners.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1135\" height=\"874\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-63861\" src=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Kadenze-Partners.png\" alt=\"Kadenze Partners\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Kadenze-Partners.png 1135w, https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Kadenze-Partners-300x231.png 300w, https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Kadenze-Partners-768x591.png 768w, https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/08\/Kadenze-Partners-1024x789.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1135px) 100vw, 1135px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2>New Courses<\/h2>\n<p>Kadenze has also announced four new courses, one from each new partner and two from\u00a0California College of the Arts (CCA).<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/mooc\/6800\/kadenze-the-art-of-cinematic-storytelling-first-steps\"><b>The Art of Cinematic Storytelling: First Steps<\/b><\/a><br \/>\n<i>California College of the Arts via Kadenze<br \/>\n<\/i>This course is an introduction to the methods of cinematic storytelling, with an emphasis on visual grammar and techniques.<br \/>\n<b> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.kadenze.com\/courses\/the-art-of-cinematic-storytelling-first-steps-i\/info?utm_campaign=gotocourse&amp;utm_medium=coursepage&amp;utm_source=classcentral\" target=\"_blank\">Go To Class<\/a><\/b><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/mooc\/6801\/kadenze-introduction-to-3d-modeling-and-animation-with-maya-tradition-meets-technology\"><b>Introduction to 3D Modeling and Animation with Maya: Tradition Meets Technology<\/b><\/a><br \/>\n<i>California College of the Arts via Kadenze<br \/>\n<\/i>Students will learn an overview of the artist workflow as it relates to modeling, texturing, animation, lighting,\u00a0and rendering. This course offers a new dimension to the process of filmmaking and design.<br \/>\n<b> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.kadenze.com\/courses\/introduction-to-3d-modeling-and-animation-with-maya-tradition-meets-technology-i\/info?utm_campaign=gotocourse&amp;utm_medium=coursepage&amp;utm_source=classcentral\" target=\"_blank\">Go To Class<\/a>\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/mooc\/6802\/kadenze-sound-design-with-kontakt\"><b>Sound Design with Kontakt<\/b><\/a><br \/>\n<i>Berklee College of Music via Kadenze<br \/>\n<\/i>This four-session course explores a practical approach to composing and producing music with Native Instruments Kontakt.<br \/>\n<b> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.kadenze.com\/courses\/sound-design-with-kontakt-i\/info?utm_campaign=gotocourse&amp;utm_medium=coursepage&amp;utm_source=classcentral\" target=\"_blank\">Go To Class<\/a>\u00a0<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/mooc\/6803\/kadenze-the-history-of-music-production-techniques\"><b>The History of Music Production Techniques<\/b><\/a><br \/>\n<i>Columbia University via Kadenze<br \/>\n<\/i>Over the past fifteen years, many of the music industry\u2019s greatest artists have made public valuable information about how they created their iconic sounds. Through the release of memoirs and interviews, their techniques \u2014 once considered closely-guarded industry secrets and the keys to their success \u2014 are now available to anyone who wants to use them.<br \/>\n<b> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.kadenze.com\/courses\/the-history-of-music-production-techniques-i\/info?utm_campaign=gotocourse&amp;utm_medium=coursepage&amp;utm_source=classcentral\" target=\"_blank\">Go To Class<\/a><\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kadenze gains two new partner institutions and simultaneously announces four new MOOCs, which focus on filmmaking and audio production.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":63861,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[103],"tags":[437],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.3 (Yoast SEO v18.5.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Columbia University and Berklee College of Music join Kadenze<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Kadenze gains two new partner institutions and simultaneously announces four new MOOCs, which focus on filmmaking and audio production.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/kadenze-columbia-berklee\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Columbia University And Berklee College Of Music Join Kadenze\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Kadenze gains two new partner institutions and simultaneously announces four new MOOCs, which focus on filmmaking and audio production.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.classcentral.com\/report\/kadenze-columbia-berklee\/\" \/>\